messages.title: WARNING
messages.content: DON'T RISK GETTING A TORY MP AND HANDING POWER BACK TO THE TORIES. Only Labour can stop the Tories. Only Labour is fighting to protect your family. Staying at home, voting Lib Dem or any other party, will let the Tories win.
Vote Lib Dem or stay at home and you risk a Tory MP and a Tory Government. Only Labour can beat the Tories.

mentions.tacticalSituation: Staying at home, voting Lib Dem or any other party, will let the Tories win.

issues.immigration: The Lib Dems want an amnesty for illegal immigrants.
issues.socialWelfare: And, like the Tories, the Lib Dems would cut Child Tax Credits and Child Trust Funds. The Tories and Lib Dems offer a coalition of cuts for our kids.

quotes.text: Nick Clegg goes public on coalition and looks to the Conservatives
